__NOTOC__
=Clean and Thrifty=

==Summary==

A simple and clean Scouting theme for WordPress.

With the best of the authors understanding, this theme is provided under any jurisdiction of public domain, free of charge, and without warranty. Modifications do not have to be made public, but it is encouraged.

It follows the [http://www.scouting.org/scoutsource/BrandGuide.aspx BSA Brand Identity Guide].

A live example can be seen at [http://troop1865.org Troop 1865's web page]

==Details==

===Page Templates===

====News====

The news page template is intended to be a blank page that displays post in the 'News' category. This makes for an ideal front page to display important informaiton.

===Images===

This theme contains minor changes to the official BSA images. All the changes are documented here.

====Boy Scout Universal Emblem Trademark====

[http://www.scouting.org/filestore/marketing/Brand/BSA_Black.jpg Original]
* Replaced white background with transparent.
* Saved as PNG.

====BSA Stationery Action Folio====

[http://www.scouting.org/filestore/marketing/images/ActionFolio_blue.png Original]
* Minor image modification so it can loop.

===Credits===

[http://www.scouting.org/ Scouting]

[http://www.cssstickyfooter.com/using-sticky-footer-code.html Sticky Footer Code]


